channel.title: Moparscape Freezes in a Black Screen? Help!
channel.description:
When I put my Moparscape on, I log in and then there comes: Loading Please wait.... And I can't press a thing, so i've guessed that my Java was bad. BUT. I have the latest Java for this time and I don't know what to do.. I mean I have a server to watch after etc. I'd be great full if someone could help me.
Thanks, Footee.
